        public AggregateClass<?> asAggregateClass(java.lang.Class<? extends Aggregate> cls)
        Obtains an instance of aggregate class information.

        If the passed class was not added to the model before, it would be added as the result of this method call.

        Throws:
        DuplicateCommandHandlerError - if there is the aggregate class handles one or more commands that are handled by another class, which was added to the model before calling this method
